rComments: Probably the greatest Prof of all time at UofT in general. Cares about the students and does not let you go wrong in any part of the course. Helps you through discussion which is the hardest part of the course. Overall amazing prof and person

The course is time consuming but very rewarding. You must prepare well for discussions. Make sure you understand concepts and not just memorize theory as you will be caught! Samer is very approachable and is always willing to help. He replies to emails quickly and will go through your excel files to help you with calculations.
Samer is a great prof. He really cares about his teaching, his students and that we come out of the course learning something useful. Love the discussion sessions - keeps you on your toes.
